sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Vue client Angular
    participant Support as Vue support Angular
    participant WS as Endpoint WebSocket /ws-chat
    participant Controller as ChatMessageController
    participant Service as ChatService
    participant Topic as Topic /topic/conversations.{conversationId}

    Note over Client,Support: Les deux vues ouvrent une connexion WebSocket vers /ws-chat

    Client->>WS: Connexion WebSocket
    Support->>WS: Connexion WebSocket

    Client->>Topic: Abonnement a /topic/conversations.{conversationId}
    Support->>Topic: Abonnement a /topic/conversations.{conversationId}

    Client->>WS: publish /app/chat.send
    WS->>Controller: Transmet le message entrant
    Controller->>Service: addMessage(conversationId, senderRole, senderId, body)
    Service-->>Controller: Message enrichi avec id et sentAt
    Controller->>Topic: Diffuse le message
    Topic-->>Client: Message temps reel
    Topic-->>Support: Message temps reel

    Controller->>Topic: Diffuse aussi le resume de conversation
